  <section id="profile" class="profile">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="profile__wrapper">
        <div class="profile__item--title">
          <p class="overline--32 color-yellow">
            Profile
          </p>
          <h3>A passionate heart with an instinct for racing</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="profile__item--description">
          <div class="profile__item--text">
            <p class="body1">
              Markas Silkunas is a name that is increasingly being heard in the karting world. Young, ambitious and full
              of passion for racing, he has already attracted attention with his perseverance, character and exceptional
              talent. From the very first days behind the wheel of a kart, it became clear that speed is his element,
              and
              the track is the place where he truly reveals himself.
            </p>
            <p class="body1">
              Markas is not just an athlete, he is a master who is constantly improving his skills. His approach to
              racing
              is a combination of technical precision, strategic thinking, and an intuitive sense of the track. He
              understands that success in karting is not only about speed, but also about attention to detail, analysis
              of
              rivals, and readiness to adapt to any conditions on the track.
            </p>
            <p class="body1">
              Markas' specialty is his ability to work hard. He is not afraid of challenges and sees every race as an
              opportunity to learn something new. From training to competition, he works to stay competitive in any
              situation. His endurance and determination help him to overcome difficulties, and his thirst for victory
              motivates him to move forward even when the situation seems difficult.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="profile__item--photo">

            <video class="img-responsive" src="/img/video/video_2025-02-17_10-44-25.mp4" autoplay loop muted></video>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="profile__item--description">
          <div class="profile__item--photo">
            <picture>
              <source srcset="/img/photo/profile_1.webp" type="image/webp">
              <img class="img-responsive" src="img/photo/profile_1.png" alt="profile photo" loading="lazy">
            </picture>
          </div>

          <div class="profile__item--text">
            <p class="body1">
              But Markas is not only about speed and victories. His support for the team, communication with colleagues
              and friendliness on the track create an image of an athlete who deserves respect not only for his
              achievements, but also for his humanity. He knows how to inspire others, remaining an example for younger
              drivers who are just starting their way in karting.
            </p>
            <p class="body1">
              Markas' main strength is his desire to develop. He does not rest on his laurels, but constantly moves
              forward, setting new goals and going beyond his own capabilities. Each season is a new chapter for him,
              filled with challenges, opportunities and chances to prove that he deserves to be among the best.
            </p>
            <p class="body1">
              Markas Silkunas is a name that is associated with speed, skill and a relentless thirst for improvement.
              His
              story is just beginning, but it promises to be bright and inspiring.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
